name: Holo-w
description: A relic. Hidden where only the earliest of pioneers will find it. 28 Tokens to represent Movement, Focus, and Energy. 28 lightning bolts. 4-Dimensional, wavelike noise patterns. Neon and Glass rendered in Cycles featuring a manifold shader Artifact and Adjacent Color Arrangement. As soon as all 28 tokens are collected a key will be revealed! These pioneers, on completion will be the first key holders!
